show.description: Two guys. One’s a master of tall tales, the other’s a master of side-eye. In each bite-sized episode, an everyday moment spirals into absurdity as one man spins wild stories to sound wiser than he is, while his unimpressed friend listens, judges, and occasionally calls the bluff. A comedy rooted in banter, bluffing, and the brilliance of doing absolutely nothing.
